Package: oroborus
Version: 1.14.0
Revision: 4
BuildDepends: dlcompat-dev
Depends: x11
Source: http://www.kensden.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/Oroborus/files/%n-%v.tar.gz
Patch: %f.patch
CompileScript: make CC=cc PREFIX=%p
InstallScript: <<
 make install PREFIX=%p DESTDIR=%d
 chmod 644 %i/share/doc/%n/doc/*.htm
 mkdir -p %i/share/gnome/wm-properties
 install -c -m 644 Oroborus1.desktop %i/share/gnome/wm-properties/
<<
DocFiles: README LICENSE CHANGES
#
Description: Alternate Window Manager
DescDetail: <<
Oroborus is yet another minimalistic but themeable window manager. In
version 1, themes can only change the look, but not functionality or
placement of widgets.
<<
DescPackaging: <<
fixed a bug that caused oroborus to suck up major amounts of system power
<<
